      <td>Instrumentalness</td>
      <td>Predicts whether a track contains no vocals. "Ooh" and "aah" sounds are treated as instrumental in this context. The closer the instrumentalness value is to 1.0, the greater likelihood the track contains no vocal content.</td>
    </tr>
